  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "## Ransomware Live Workbook\n<p align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://ransomware.live/ransomwarelive.png\" alt=\"logo\" style=\"width:200px\"></a>\n</p>\n---\n [Ransomware.live](https://ransomware.live/#/about) is a ransomware groups observatory based on ransomwatch and inspired by ransomlook.It is a ransomware leak site monitoring tool. It will scrape all of the entries on various ransomware leak sites. \n\nThe workbook is a collaboration between [Gavin Knapp](https://github.com/m4nbat) and [Chiheb Chebbi](https://github.com/chihebchebbi)"
      },
      "name": "text - 2"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "let victims = externaldata(\n        victim:string,\n        country:string,\n        domain:string,\n        title:string,\n        summary:string,\n        url:string,\n        added:string,)\n[h@\"https://api.ransomware.live/allcyberattacks\"]\nwith(format=\"multijson\",ignoreFirstRecord=false);\nvictims\n| summarize count()",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Total Victims",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "gridSettings": {
          "formatters": [
            {
              "columnMatch": "victim",
              "formatter": 18,
              "formatOptions": {
                "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                "thresholdsGrid": [
                  {
                    "operator": "Default",
                    "thresholdValue": null,
                    "representation": "Pre attack",
                    "text": "{0}{1}"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "columnMatch": "url",
              "formatter": 18,
              "formatOptions": {
